    Product specifications :

    • Size: 25x20x10 mm
    • Material: Polystyrene (synthetic aromatic polymer made from the monomer= styrene, a liquid petrochemical; one of the most widely used plastics= )
    • Production: according to the European standard EN 71 specifies safety r= equirements for toys, also directive 2005/84/EG (Phthalate)
    • Made in Europe
    • Weight: 1.4 gr. per piece
    • Price per piece; scale price per colour
    • Colours: red, green, blue, white, orange, brown

    This product contains environmen= tal unfriendly plastics. 1 cent per product will be collected and put towar= ds charity at the end of the year. The sum is divided 50/50 between Sea She= pherd and Ocean Cleanup.
